N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 9606.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

The purpose of these guidelines is to provide the criteria
and procedures by which the authority makes determinations to approve, deny or
revoke its certification of minority or women owned business
enterprises. Notes
